    "description": "Allen Career Institute Asia Pacific Associates, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Curriculum Developer for our Hyderabad operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Allen Career Institute Asia Pacific Associates:\nAllen Career Institute Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Create curriculum-aligned learning materials and assessments\n• Maintain classroom discipline and create a positive learning environment\n• Maintain student records and prepare progress reports\n• Design formative and summative assessments aligned to learning objectives\n• Participate in teacher training and professional development programs\n• Utilize technology and digital tools to enhance learning outcomes\n• Conduct doubt-clearing sessions and remedial classes for weak students\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Student Assessment\n• Proficiency in Classroom Management\n• Proficiency in Mentoring\n• Proficiency in Educational Technology\n• Proficiency in Research Skills\n• Proficiency in Bloom's Taxonomy\n• Proficiency in E-learning\n• Proficiency in Special Education\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Flexible working hours\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Hyderabad, Telangana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Allen Career Institute Asia Pacific Associates!",
